Classifier, Property
public abstract class Decoratable<S extends Stereotype> extends PackageableElement
A model element that can be decorated with a stereotype to identify its ontological properties according to the Unified Foundational Ontology (UFO). Examples include a class decorated with the stereotype "kind" identifying it as a type of object that provides an identity principle to its instances.
